div.p:
The reſt have um, viz. pes, pedum (whence bipes; bipedum) praes, praedum; mos, morum; flos, florum; thus, thurum; crus, crurum; ſus, ſuum; grus, gruum; 

                        Mr. Farnaby ſaith pus, purunis 
                     laus, laudum; fraus, fraudum; bos, boum (by a Syncope for bovium.)
